size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">39</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":39,\"repo\":\"cobenian/inet_cidr\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Classless Inter-Domain Routing (CIDR) for Elixir that is compatible with :inet and supports both IPv4 and IPv6.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T13:06:35.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-foss/awesome-sysadmin","categoryHTML":"<h2>Monitoring</h2><h3>Metric &#x26; Metric Collection</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Collectors only\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/python-diamond/Diamond\">Diamond</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/python-diamond/Diamond\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1685,\"repo\":\"python-diamond/Diamond\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Python based statistic collection daemon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://collectd.org/\">Collectd</a> - System statistic collection daemon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://collectl.sourceforge.net/\">Collectl</a> - High precision system performance metrics collecting tool.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/zalando/PGObserver\">PGObserver</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/zalando/PGObserver\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">310</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":310,\"repo\":\"zalando/PGObserver\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Monitoring solution for PostgreSQL databases that also works with AWS RDS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/etsy/statsd/\">Statsd</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/etsy/statsd/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":16703,\"repo\":\"etsy/statsd\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Application statistic listener.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://opentsdb.net/docs/build/html/user_guide/utilities/tcollector.html\">tcollector</a> - System statistic collection daemon written in Python for OpenTSDB</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/influxdata/telegraf\">Telegraf</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/influxdata/telegraf\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":12066,\"repo\":\"influxdata/telegraf\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - The plugin-driven server agent for collecting &#x26; reporting metrics.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T12:00:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-foss/awesome-sysadmin","categoryHTML":"<h2>Monitoring</h2><h3>Metric &#x26; Metric Collection</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Dashboards\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://grafana.org/\">Grafana</a> - A Graphite &#x26; InfluxDB Dashboard and Graph Editor.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ganglia.sourceforge.net/\">Ganglia</a> - High performance, scalable RRD based monitoring for grids and/or clusters of servers. Compatible with Graphite using a single collection process.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://oss.oetiker.ch/rrdtool/\">RRDtool</a> - Industry standard, high performance data logging and graphing system for time series data.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://dashing.io/\">Dashing</a> - Ruby gem that allows for rapid statistical dashboard development. An all HTML5 approach allows for big screen displays in data centers or conference rooms.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://facette.io\">Facette</a> - Time series data visualization and graphing software written in Go.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Freeboard/freeboard\">Freeboard</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Freeboard/freeboard\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.3k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":6292,\"repo\":\"Freeboard/freeboard\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A damn-sexy front-end real-time dashboard for the internet of things. Transforms raw JSON into delicious UI.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T12:00:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-foss/awesome-sysadmin","categoryHTML":"<h2>Monitoring</h2><h3>Metric &#x26; Metric Collection</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Storage\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://opentsdb.net/\">OpenTSDB</a> - Store and server massive amounts of time series data without losing granularity.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/kairosdb/kairosdb\">KairosDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/kairosdb/kairosdb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1670,\"repo\":\"kairosdb/kairosdb\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Fast distributed scalable time series database, fork of OpenTSDB 1.x.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://influxdb.com/\">InfluxDB</a> - Distributed time series database with no external dependencies.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T12:00:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"awesome-foss/awesome-sysadmin","categoryHTML":"<h2>Monitoring</h2><h3>Metric &#x26; Metric Collection</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Packages\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://graphite.readthedocs.org/en/latest/\">Graphite</a> - Scalable graphing server.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.elastic.co/products/beats\">Packetbeat</a> - Captures network traffic and displays it in a custom Kibana dashboard for easy viewing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://prometheus.io/\">Prometheus</a> - Service monitoring system and time series database.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/VictoriaMetrics/VictoriaMetrics\">VictoriaMetrics</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/VictoriaMetrics/VictoriaMetrics\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7.3k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":7267,\"repo\":\"VictoriaMetrics/VictoriaMetrics\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Service monitoring system and time series database.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T12:00:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"fasouto/awesome-dataviz","categoryHTML":"<h2>R tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://hafen.github.io/rbokeh/\">rbokeh</a> - R Interface to Bokeh.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T11:53:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"fasouto/awesome-dataviz","categoryHTML":"<h2>R tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/rgl/index.html\">rgl</a> - 3D Visualization Using OpenGL</li>","updatedAt":"2015-07-30T11:53:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"javierluraschi/awesome-dataviz","categoryHTML":"<h2>R tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://cran.r-project.o